data.description:
SELLER IS OFFERING TO PAY UP TO $3000 OF BUYER'S CLOSING COSTS/PRE-PAIDS/ RATE BUY DOWN WITH AN ACCEPTABLE OFFER!! location! Location! Location! This well cared for home is conveniently located within walking distance to the bank, Walmart and many in-town restaurants. When I say well cared for, I seriously mean that this home has been loved by proud homeowners who not only have a weekly cleaning regiment, they also have replaced, fixed, redone, updated all the big ticket items as well as many more! This list includes: roof, HVAC, gutter guard, and oversized double hung windows. (See full list attached).
This home has a nice open/split floor plan with 3 beds and 2 full baths. The eat-in kitchen has an island/bar with sink, making it convenient for entertaining guests. The utility room is off the kitchen and has room for pantry shelves. The two car attached garage may be hidden from the road but it has great space for working and Don’t forget this garage has 220! The seller is a master gardener and works all spring and summer on the established flower beds and trees which makes the yard gorgeous in the spring and summer. This home is a must see! Don’t just drive by! Call your agent to view it! THIS HOME IS USDA eligible, TALK TO YOUR LOAN OFFICER ABOUT 100% FINANCING! Sq ft & rm sz approx.
